cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the DMRS type A position to an invalid value '2' will cause a configuration error in the physical layer setup, leading to failure in downlink signal transmission.
du.explanation_zh: 將 DMRS 類型 A 位置設定為無效值 '2' 會在物理層設定中導致配置錯誤，從而導致下行鏈路信號傳輸失敗。
